episodes.title: Searching for Taylor Casey: My Trip to the Bahamas to Find Her
episodes.description:
In this episode, I travel to the Bahamas in search of my friend, Taylor Casey, who mysteriously disappeared from Paradise Island on the evening of July 19th, 2024. I distribute flyers and try to piece together any clues 🕵️‍♀️ that may lead to answers about her disappearance.

🔔 Please note: I do not hold the yoga ashram responsible for her disappearance. If you have any tips, clues, or ideas on how we can spread her story further, please email me at jessicasavanotravels@gmail.com

Yoga Centers in India that I recommend:

Rishikesh Yoga Teacher Training -Rishikesh, India
Tattvaa Yogashala - Rishikesh, India
Pyramid Yogshala - Rishikesh, India 
Nath Yoga Shala - Rishikesh, India

Contact my dear friend/yogi Harshvardhan on IG as he does traveling yogic programs @yogatman
